#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:19
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "<strong class=\"text-slate-900\">Global Pixel War</strong> is a real-time "
#| "collaborative canvas. Each registered player can place <strong "
#| "class=\"text-slate-900\">one pixel every 60 seconds</strong>. Every "
#| "placement is queued, validated, and then broadcast live via WebSocket to "
#| "every connected player. Work together — or compete — to claim space on "
#| "the shared canvas."
msgid ""
"<strong class=\"text-slate-900\">Pixo Canvo</strong> is a real-time "
"collaborative canvas. Each registered player can place <strong class=\"text-"
"slate-900\">one pixel every 60 seconds</strong>. Every placement is queued, "
"validated, and then broadcast live via WebSocket to every connected player. "
"Work together — or compete — to claim space on the shared canvas."
msgstr ""
"<strong class=\"text-slate-900\">Perang Piksel Global</strong> adalah kanvas "
"kolaboratif waktu nyata. Setiap pemain terdaftar dapat menempatkan <strong "
"class=\"text-slate-900\">satu piksel setiap 60 detik</strong>. Setiap "
"penempatan diantri, divalidasi, dan kemudian disiarkan langsung melalui "
"WebSocket ke setiap pemain yang terhubung. Bekerja sama — atau bersaing — "
"untuk mendapatkan ruang di kanvas bersama."

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:31
msgid "Placing pixels"
msgstr "Menempatkan piksel"

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:37
msgid "Pick a color from the palette"
msgstr "Pilih warna dari palet"

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:38
msgid ""
"Choose from the 21-color palette at the top of the Canvas page. Use the "
"<strong>Custom Color</strong> picker next to the palette for any hex color "
"you like. Your active selection is highlighted with a ring."
msgstr ""
"Pilih dari palet 21 warna di bagian atas halaman Canvas. Gunakan pemilih "
"<strong>Warna Khusus</strong> di sebelah palet untuk warna hex apa pun yang "
"Anda suka. Pilihan aktif Anda disorot dengan cincin."

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:44
msgid "Zoom and navigate"
msgstr "Perbesar dan navigasikan"

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:45
msgid ""
"Use the <strong>+</strong> and <strong>−</strong> buttons to zoom. Pan by "
"scrolling or dragging. The ⛶ button enters full-screen mode for a "
"distraction-free experience. Zoom in before placing to avoid missing your "
"target cell."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan tombol <strong>+</strong> dan <strong>−</strong> untuk memperbesar. "
"Geser dengan menggulir atau menyeret. Tombol ⛶ memasuki mode layar penuh "
"untuk pengalaman bebas gangguan. Perbesar sebelum menempatkan untuk "
"menghindari kehilangan sel target Anda."

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:51
msgid "Click to place"
msgstr "Klik untuk menempatkan"

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:52
msgid ""
"Click any cell on the canvas while a color is selected. Your placement is "
"sent to the server, validated (cooldown, bounds, auth), and if accepted it "
"appears on every connected player's screen within milliseconds."
msgstr ""
"Klik sel mana pun di kanvas saat warna dipilih. Penempatan Anda dikirim ke "
"server, divalidasi (cooldown, batas, autentikasi), dan jika diterima, "
"penempatan tersebut akan muncul di layar setiap pemain yang terhubung dalam "
"milidetik."

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:58
msgid "Wait out the cooldown"
msgstr "Tunggu cooldownnya"

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:59
msgid ""
"After each accepted placement you must wait <strong>60 seconds</strong> "
"before placing again. The status bar shows how long remains. Rejected "
"attempts do not reset the cooldown."
msgstr ""
"Setelah setiap penempatan yang diterima, Anda harus menunggu <strong>60 "
"detik</strong> sebelum melakukan penempatan lagi. Bilah status menunjukkan "
"berapa lama waktu yang tersisa. Upaya yang ditolak tidak akan mengatur ulang "
"cooldown."

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:65
msgid "Highlight your pixels"
msgstr "Sorot piksel Anda"

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:66
msgid ""
"Press <strong>Highlight My Pixels</strong> to dim everything else and see "
"exactly which pixels you own on the current canvas."
msgstr ""
"Tekan <strong>Sorot Piksel Saya</strong> untuk meredupkan semuanya dan "
"melihat piksel mana yang Anda miliki di kanvas saat ini."

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:75
msgid "Dynamic canvas size"
msgstr "Ukuran kanvas dinamis"

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:78
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The canvas starts at a fixed size and <strong>automatically grows</strong> "
"as more pixels are placed. Once 80 %% of cells are filled the grid expands "
"by a set number of rows and columns, up to a configured maximum. This keeps "
"the canvas competitive — there is always new space to claim."
msgstr ""
"The canvas starts at a fixed size and <strong>automatically grows</strong> "
"as more pixels are placed. Once 80 %% of cells are filled the grid expands "
"by a set number of rows and columns, up to a configured maximum. This keeps "
"the canvas competitive — there is always new space to claim."

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:93
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Beyond the global canvas you can play inside <strong>private communities</"
"strong>. Each community has its own independent canvas, leaderboard, and "
"chat room. Go to the <a href=\"%(communities_url)s\" class=\"font-semibold "
"text-amber-600 hover:text-amber-800\">Communities</a> page to manage yours."
msgstr ""
"Beyond the global canvas you can play inside <strong>private communities</"
"strong>. Each community has its own independent canvas, leaderboard, and "
"chat room. Go to the <a href=\"%(communities_url)s\" class=\"font-semibold "
"text-amber-600 hover:text-amber-800\">Communities</a> page to manage yours."

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:102
msgid "Creating a community"
msgstr "Menciptakan komunitas"

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:103
msgid ""
"Any logged-in user can create <strong>one community</strong>. Enter a name "
"and click <em>Create community</em>. A URL-friendly slug is generated "
"automatically. You become the owner and are added as the first member."
msgstr ""
"Setiap pengguna yang masuk dapat membuat <strong>satu komunitas</strong>. "
"Masukkan nama dan klik <em>Buat komunitas</em>. Siput ramah URL dihasilkan "
"secara otomatis. Anda menjadi pemilik dan ditambahkan sebagai anggota "
"pertama."

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:109
msgid "Inviting members"
msgstr "Mengundang anggota"

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:110
msgid ""
"Click <em>Invitation link</em> on any community card to open a popup with a "
"shareable URL. Anyone who opens that link and is logged in will be added to "
"the community immediately."
msgstr ""
"Klik <em>Tautan undangan</em> di kartu komunitas mana pun untuk membuka "
"munculan dengan URL yang dapat dibagikan. Siapa pun yang membuka tautan itu "
"dan masuk akan segera ditambahkan ke komunitas."

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:116
msgid "Leaving a community"
msgstr "Meninggalkan komunitas"

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:117
msgid ""
"Members can leave any community they did not create. Click <em>Leave "
"community</em> and confirm. The owner cannot leave — they must delete the "
"community instead."
msgstr ""
"Anggota dapat meninggalkan komunitas mana pun yang tidak mereka buat. Klik "
"<em>Keluar dari komunitas</em> dan konfirmasi. Pemiliknya tidak dapat keluar "
"— mereka harus menghapus komunitas tersebut."

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:123
msgid "Deleting a community"
msgstr "Menghapus komunitas"

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:124
msgid ""
"Only the owner can delete a community. Click <em>Delete community</em> and "
"confirm. This permanently removes the community, all its pixels, chat "
"messages, and membership records — it cannot be undone."
msgstr ""
"Hanya pemilik yang dapat menghapus komunitas. Klik <em>Hapus komunitas</em> "
"dan konfirmasi. Tindakan ini akan menghapus komunitas, semua pikselnya, "
"pesan chat, dan catatan keanggotaannya secara permanen — tindakan ini tidak "
"dapat dibatalkan."

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:130
msgid "Community details page"
msgstr "Halaman detail komunitas"

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:131
msgid ""
"Click <em>Community details</em> on any card to open a dedicated page "
"showing: community info, a live canvas preview (click to enlarge), and a "
"sortable member table with each member's join date and pixel count."
msgstr ""
"Klik <em>Rincian komunitas</em> di kartu mana pun untuk membuka laman khusus "
"yang menampilkan: info komunitas, pratinjau kanvas langsung (klik untuk "
"memperbesar), dan tabel anggota yang dapat diurutkan dengan tanggal "
"bergabung setiap anggota dan jumlah piksel."

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:140
msgid "Leaderboard & chat"
msgstr "Papan peringkat & obrolan"

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:146
#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/leaders.html:4
msgid "Ranking"
msgstr ""

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:147
#, fuzzy, python-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <a href=\"%(leaders_url)s\" class=\"font-semibold text-fuchsia-600 "
#| "hover:text-fuchsia-800\">Top Players</a> page ranks every contributor by "
#| "the number of accepted pixels currently on the canvas. The list is "
#| "available for the global canvas and for each community you belong to."
msgid ""
"The <a href=\"%(leaders_url)s\" class=\"font-semibold text-fuchsia-600 "
"hover:text-fuchsia-800\">Ranking</a> page ranks every contributor by the "
"number of accepted pixels currently on the canvas. The list is available for "
"the global canvas and for each community you belong to."
msgstr ""
"The <a href=\"%(leaders_url)s\" class=\"font-semibold text-fuchsia-600 "
"hover:text-fuchsia-800\">Top Players</a> page ranks every contributor by the "
"number of accepted pixels currently on the canvas. The list is available for "
"the global canvas and for each community you belong to."

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:153
msgid "Live chat"
msgstr "Obrolan langsung"

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:154
msgid ""
"Each canvas has a live chat sidebar. Toggle it with the floating button in "
"the bottom-right corner. Logged-in users can send messages; everyone can "
"read them. Community chat is scoped — messages in one community are not "
"visible in another."
msgstr ""
"Setiap kanvas memiliki sidebar obrolan langsung. Alihkan dengan tombol "
"mengambang di sudut kanan bawah. Pengguna yang masuk dapat mengirim pesan; "
"semua orang bisa membacanya. Obrolan komunitas tercakup — pesan di satu "
"komunitas tidak terlihat di komunitas lain."

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:162
msgid "Your account"
msgstr "Akun Anda"

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:164
msgid ""
"Click your <strong>avatar</strong> in the top navigation to open Profile "
"Settings."
msgstr ""
"Klik <strong>avatar</strong> Anda di navigasi atas untuk membuka Pengaturan "
"Profil."

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:165
msgid ""
"Change your <strong>username</strong>, upload a custom <strong>avatar</"
"strong>, or update your <strong>password</strong> at any time."
msgstr ""
"Ubah <strong>namapengguna</strong> Anda, unggah <strong>avatar</strong> "
"khusus, atau perbarui <strong>kata sandi</strong> Anda kapan saja."

#: pixelwar/templates/pixelwar/guide.html:166
msgid ""
"You must be logged in to place pixels, send chat messages, create or join "
"communities."
msgstr ""
"Anda harus masuk untuk menempatkan piksel, mengirim pesan obrolan, membuat "
"atau bergabung dengan komunitas."

